-- Gold May Reach $1,500 an Ounce by Christmas, Petropavlovsk's Hambro Says
-- B y   A m a n d a   J o r d a n
-- 2010-10-05T05:22:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-05/gold-may-reach-1-500-an-ounce-by-christmas-petropavlovsk-s-hambro-says.html
Gold prices could reach $1,500 an
ounce by Christmas, according to the chairman of Petropavlovsk
Plc, Russia’s third-largest producer of the metal.  Gold may even rise to $2,500 an ounce “in a year or so,”
Peter Hambro said today in a Bloomberg Television interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
